data.title: GIR: Rio Cobre view in Spanish Town
data.meta_description:
As Jamaica's residents continue to document Tropical Storm Nicole's impact, The Gleaner has received footage from the eastern end of Spanish Town that depicts an aggressive Rio Cobre river.
